         Bigraph Evaluator & Rewriting

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 REQUIREMENTS:

  *  OCaml >= 4.0.0
  *  findlib
  *  ocp-build
  *  camlMiniSat
  *  Graphviz

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 INSTALL:

  > ./configure
  > make 
  > make install

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 UNINSTALL:

  > make uninstall

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 VIA OPAM:

  > opam repository add dcs http://dcs.gla.ac.uk/~michele/dcs-opam-repository
  > opam install bigrapher

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 NOTES:

  *  Use gmake instead of make on BSD systems.